  "details": "A weakness has been identified in UTT HiPER 1200GW up to 2.5.3-170306. Affected is an unknown function of the file /goform/formPptpClientConfig of the component Web Management Interface. This manipulation of the argument PPTP server address/username/password/tunnel name causes stack-based buffer overflow. The attack may be initiated remotely. The exploit has been made available to the public and could be used for attacks.",
